# flutter_rust_bridge
# NOTE: the generated Dart bindings (frb_generated*.dart) ARE committed — a
# pub.dev package must ship all its Dart source (you can't run Rust→Dart codegen
# at pub-get time), and CI builds from a clean checkout. Regenerate with
# `flutter_rust_bridge_codegen generate` after any Rust API change.

